      "2. Develop the proposed geometric diagnostics framework to analyze the curvature and stability of layers during quantization.",
      "3. Compare the performance of quantized models using the baseline versus the geometric diagnostics approach across standard datasets (e.g., ImageNet, CIFAR-10).",
      "4. Evaluate the models based on accuracy, inference speed, and resource usage, documenting improvements in the trade-off between performance and complexity."
    ],
    "Risk Factors and Limitations": "Potential risks include the challenge of accurately modeling the geometric properties of complex neural network architectures, which may vary significantly. Additionally, the proposed framework may require careful calibration to ensure the effectiveness of the geometric diagnostics in practice, which could introduce additional complexity."
  }
}
