    "Related Work": "Existing works like 'Rate Distortion For Model Compression' explore fundamental limits, but they do not utilize dynamic mutual information as a lever for real-time adaptation of compression strategies. This proposal directly integrates mutual information dynamics across layers with compression techniques, providing a new perspective on achieving optimal compression rates.",
