The proposed research idea thus aims to bridge this gap by introducing a comprehensive framework specifically designed for kernel-level optimization of mixed-precision quantization tailored for GPU architectures. This framework will not only focus on mixed-precision configurations but will also emphasize hardware-specific optimizations that can be profiled and traced for real-time performance validation.

