A new proposal can focus on simplifying the approach to mixed-precision quantization while keeping a strong emphasis on hardware performance metrics. The core idea is to leverage a straightforward, empirical approach to determine the optimal bit-width per layer using a profiling-based method that directly correlates performance metrics to quantization decisions.

