- **Feasibility**: The proposed experiments are straightforward and can be conducted with existing machine learning frameworks and datasets, making it practical for an academic setting. The reliance on local entropy estimates aligns well with existing methodologies in rate-distortion theory.

- **Clarity**: The proposal is structured clearly, with each section addressing the core components of the research idea. It articulates a well-defined hypothesis and outlines specific experiments that will validate this hypothesis.

Overall, this refined proposal aligns well with the methodological preferences and focuses on quantifiable outcomes that can be published in top-tier ML conferences.
